title.rendered: I KALL Z1 Smartphone (4GB, 32GB, 4G Volte, Dual Sim) (Sky Blue)

content.rendered:
• 8MP Rear Camera | 5MP Front Camera | Made in India
  • 13.84 cm (5.5 inch) Display | multi-touch capacitive touch screen with 480×960 pixel resolution
  • 4GB ram, 32GB storage | Expandable Memory 64GB | Dual Sim | 4G Volte
  • Android 8.1 with 1.3 Ghz Quad Core
  • 1 Year warranty for mobile and 6 Months for box accessories
